title: Any update on clubs?
body: It's been almost a year now since I'v been able to see my club. All other members can still access the club and represent it fine, it's just me.

replies.body: Sometimes a club might lose sync and not appear for the leader.  Toss me the name of your club, and I'll see if I can refresh it for you.
Booped!  Your club should be sync'd now.  :D
